# IVF-specific secrets (DO NOT COMMIT)
# Use User Secrets (dotnet user-secrets) or environment variables in production
# For local development:
#   1. Create appsettings.local.json (git-ignored)
#   2. Or use: dotnet user-secrets set "Monitoring:PrometheusAuth" "..."
